  m_Name: tut_seconddraft
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialStep
  id: seconddraft
  text: "The hearts up top measure your CONFIDENCE. It's basically your health +
    currency. \n\nEach card has a difference CONFIDENCE cost to play, displayed on
    each card. \n\nPlaying cards will affect Daisy's CHARM and further impact your
    CONFIDENCE - positively or negativley - depending on current CHARM and CONFIDENCE
    levels.\n\nA card's impact is always hidden. Pay attention to how Luke speaks
    and how Daisy responds. Experiment.\n\nYou'll need not only high enough CONFIDENCE
    to ask Daisy to the dance, but Daisy will need to be CHARMED enough to say yes.\n "
  boxSize: {x: 600, y: 300}
  boxAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  dismissMode: 0
  showBackdrop: 1
